# Cursor Rule — Business Rules

Voucher can be sold only after admin approval.
Sale price must be lower than original price.
Voucher code is issued only after successful simulated payment.
Each voucher code must be unique.
Used/expired/cancelled/locked codes cannot be redeemed.
Partner can redeem only codes for own voucher/branch/program.
Sold quantity must not exceed issued quantity.
Critical operations must create audit logs.
